{
  "texts": [
    "It sometimes seemed, as if this was the MLMs way of saying: \"I have no idea\".",
    "The ability to confess being unknowledgeable is lacking in all models but GPT Neo X.Filtering to avoid biases seems rather undesirable.",
    "It would be better to train the model for desirable answers.",
    "Not only ChatGPT with filtering, but also StableLM and WizardLM without any filtering showed signs of trying to teach the user, e.g.",
    "in preaching healthy living styles without smoking when being asked about wildfires that are caused by smokers."
  ]
}